# Poll: Add ETH-B as a Collateral Type - August 10, 2020

The Maker Foundation Interim Risk Team has placed a Governance Poll into the [voting system](https://vote.makerdao.com/polling) through which the community can signal their support to add USDC-B as a collateral type.

The proposed initial Risk Parameters for ETH-B are:

- Stability Fee: 50%
- Debt Ceiling: 10,000,000
- Liquidation Ratio: 120%
- Auction Lot Size: 50,000 USDC
- Minimum Bid Increment: 3%
- Bid Duration: 6 hours
- Max Auction Duration: 3 days
- Liquidation Penalty: 13%
- Dust: 20 Dai

This Governance Poll ([FAQ](https://community-development.makerdao.com/makerdao-mcd-faqs/faqs#governance)) will be active for approximately 3 days beginning on Monday, August 10 at 4:00 PM UTC.

## Review

Additional context was presented in a [Signal Request](https://forum.makerdao.com/t/3349) on July 24, 2020. Please review the discussion there to inform your position before voting.

## Next Steps

- If this proposal passes there will be an Executive Vote on Friday, August 15th asking MKR token holders if they support or reject the change.

---

